      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Future Boundary\n\nDo not over-harden the model yet.\n\nThe current implementation should preserve a later upgrade path to:\n- multi-fragment authority domains\n- tighter lifecycle/hook scoping\n- explicit cross-fragment capability surfaces\n\nBut the immediate job is simpler: make the current traversal/authority rule explicit and consistent.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
