    {
      "id": "trav-next",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Next Questions",
      "position": {
        "x": 1220,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Next Questions\n\nFollow-up questions, not blockers for this phase:\n- what should the explicit import API/UI be for raw text or HTML URLs?\n- when navigating into a non-fragment graph, what runtime state beyond focus should be preserved vs reset?\n- when multi-fragment authority domains arrive later, which of these current fragment gates should widen first?",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
